    "name": "Starbump",
    "steam_appid": 3038620,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038620/extras/de3084dcf8a5ad6fd1042c7d7f861305.avif?t=1770951670\" width=835 height=220 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>STARBUMP（星弹乱斗）</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款混乱疯狂的 4 人派对平台游戏中，把你的朋友弹飞到太空去吧——没有一段友情能全身而退！<br>Starbump 将快节奏动作、第三人称平台跳跃和竞技模式融合在色彩缤纷的世界中。你的沙发将变成发射台，准备迎接飞天软糖与破碎友谊的狂欢！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038620/extras/02c1cf14da3cc0eaddc6ccc85df2a1c4.poster.avif?t=1770951670\" width=720 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038620/extras/02c1cf14da3cc0eaddc6ccc85df2a1c4.webm?t=1770951670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⭐ 你会爱上 Starbump 的理由</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Starbump 就像是一款派对游戏、平台跳跃和物理沙盒一起爆炸后的产物。每一局都是混乱，每一次跳跃都是背叛，每一回合都会有人大喊：“再来一局！”</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4 人本地多人乱斗</strong> <br>支持 <i>Remote Play Together</i>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>基于物理引擎的疯狂体验</strong> <br>疯狂投掷、碰撞与高速弹飞！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多种游戏模式</strong> <br>竞技场、火箭球、跑酷、抢夺等。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快速对局 = 立即复仇</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>零肝度：纯乐趣，无废料</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为混乱、竞争与笑声而生的多彩世界</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038620/extras/c52479b06e509bfd9d1a7076f43e8f5d.poster.avif?t=1770951670\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038620/extras/c52479b06e509bfd9d1a7076f43e8f5d.webm?t=1770951670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎮 本地分屏多人游戏模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四大混乱模式：跑酷、竞技场、火箭球、抢夺。<br>搭配奇葩武器、物理机制关卡和绚丽的世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>跑酷（Parkour）</strong> – 通过随机生成的关卡段落冲向终点平台。掉下去就复活！第一个到达终点的人会立即结束本轮比赛。<br><strong>竞技场（Arena）</strong> – 把你的朋友撞飞出场地！使用各种古怪武器并适应每个竞技场的独特机制。混乱保证。<br><strong>火箭球（Rocketball）</strong> – 用完美时机的魔法旋转弹开火箭！每次反弹都会让它变得更快……直到有人顶不住为止。<br><strong>抢夺（Tag）</strong> – 抢到王冠并尽可能长时间守住它，而其他人会拼命来夺走！准备好迎接背叛与最后一秒的逆转吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未来将陆续添加更多模式与世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038620/extras/1de1e3ccecbea22574ccdc2050f3de34.poster.avif?t=1770951670\" width=720 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038620/extras/1de1e3ccecbea22574ccdc2050f3de34.webm?t=1770951670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>📍 我们的路线图（Roadmap）</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Early Access 阶段计划推出多达 6 种游戏模式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个可单人或合作游玩的入门冒险模式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >EA 上线时新增两个世界（火与冰），后续会通过免费更新添加更多世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Early Access：2026 年第一季度</strong>，并将在 <strong>Steam Next Fest</strong> 提供试玩 Demo。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2027 年正式版发布</strong>，带有在线多人模式与完整的故事冒险模式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未来目标：主机平台移植 + 专为在线对战设计的模式。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🧐 我们的理念</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们是两名独立开发者，所有内容均由手工打造——不使用任何 AI。<br>无内购、无付费更新、无限时物品：只需一次购买，你就能获得所有内容，就像经典复古游戏一样。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038620/extras/bb5a07c0cbbce6bbc46148609f19c759.poster.avif?t=1770951670\" width=720 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038620/extras/bb5a07c0cbbce6bbc46148609f19c759.webm?t=1770951670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
